PART 1Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî BASIC BLADE COMPONENT

1Ô∏è‚É£ Create Component

üìå Command
php artisan make:component Alert

Files Created
app/View/Components/Alert.php
resources/views/components/alert.blade.php

2Ô∏è‚É£ Component Class

app/View/Components/Alert.php

namespace App\View\Components;

use Illuminate\View\Component;

class Alert extends Component
{
    public string $type;

    public function __construct($type = 'success')
    {
        $this->type = $type;
    }

    public function render()
    {
        return view('components.alert');
    }
}

3Ô∏è‚É£ Component View (Using Slot)

resources/views/components/alert.blade.php

<div class="alert alert-{{ $type }}">
    {{ $slot }}
</div>

4Ô∏è‚É£ Use Component in Blade
<x-alert type="danger">
    Invalid credentials!
</x-alert>

PART 2Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî NAMED SLOTS (ADVANCED üî•)

1Ô∏è‚É£ Card Component
php artisan make:component Card

app/View/Components/Card.php
resources/views/components/card.blade.php

2Ô∏è‚É£ Card Blade with Named Slots

üìÑ card.blade.php

<div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
        {{ $header }}
    </div>

    <div class="card-body">
        {{ $slot }}
    </div>

    <div class="card-footer">
        {{ $footer }}
    </div>
</div>

3Ô∏è‚É£ Use Named Slots
<x-card>
    <x-slot name="header">
        Product Details
    </x-slot>

    Product description goes here...

    <x-slot name="footer">
        <button>Buy Now</button>
    </x-slot>
</x-card>

PART 3Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî PASSING DATA (PROPS)
<x-alert :type="$errorType">
    {{ $message }}
</x-alert>

PART 4Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî ANONYMOUS COMPONENTS (NO CLASS üî•)

Used for simple UI elements

1Ô∏è‚É£ Create Blade File

resources/views/components/button.blade.php

<button class="btn btn-{{ $type ?? 'primary' }}">
    {{ $slot }}
</button>

2Ô∏è‚É£ Use It
<x-button type="success">
    Save
</x-button>

PART 5Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî COMPONENT ATTRIBUTES & MERGING
<button {{ $attributes->merge(['class' => 'btn']) }}>
    {{ $slot }}
</button>


Usage:

<x-button class="btn-danger">
    Delete
</x-button>

PART 6Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî LAYOUT COMPONENT (VERY IMPORTANT üî•)

1Ô∏è‚É£ Create Layout

resources/views/components/layout.blade.php

<html>
<head>
    <title>{{ $title ?? 'App' }}</title>
</head>
<body>

<header>Navbar</header>

<main>
    {{ $slot }}
</main>

<footer>Footer</footer>

</body>
</html>

2Ô∏è‚É£ Use Layout
<x-layout title="Dashboard">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
</x-layout>

PART 7Ô∏è‚É£ ‚Äî CONDITIONAL SLOTS
@if(isset($footer))
    <div>{{ $footer }}</div>
@endif
